77
00:04:20,159 --> 00:04:21,800
Bola fyzicky napadnutá väzenkyňou,

78
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:24,029
ktorá sa nahnevala po incidente,

79
00:04:24,029 --> 00:04:25,829
