212
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,009
<i>Och, môj. Prepáčte.</i>

213
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:48,840
<i>Prosím, pokračujte.</i>

214
00:11:51,649 --> 00:11:52,679
Och, nie.

215
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:55,549
